<div class="block block--intro">
  <div class="container block__inner">
    <h1 class="h1 block__header">Partnership</h1>
        <p>Partner with Street Support Network to help homeless people in Manchester.</p>
        <a href="give-help.html">Other ways to give help</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="block">
  <div class="container block__inner">
    <div class="block__content">
    	<p>We are looking for businesses and organisations to partner with us in supporting over 30 Manchester homelessness charities and voluntary groups.</p>
    	<p>We have a list of features that organisations would like us to develop, to help them provide effective support for homeless people. Could you fund any of the following...</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Launch The Manchester Homelessness Charter: £5,000</li>
        <li>Roll out accross Greater Manchester: £6,000</li>
        <li>Apple &amp; Android app versions for use offline: £6,000 each</li>
        <li>City wide publicity campaign: £5,000</li>
        <li>One year admin role for an ex-homeless person: £9,000</li>
        <li>Public impact dashboard: £4,000</li>
        <li>Map view of organisations and services: £3,000</li>
      </ul> 

      <p>If you share our mission to support local people experiencing homelessness, could you help the Street Support Network by donating money or resources?</p>
      {{> form-feedback}}
      <!-- ko ifnot: isFormSubmitSuccessful -->
      <form class="form" data-bind="submit: submit">
        <p>Please fill in the form below to let us know what you are able to offer.</p>
        <p>* denotes a required field.</p>
        <fieldset class="form__fieldset" data-bind="with: formModel">
          <legend class="h2 form__fieldset-title">I Can Help!</legend>
          <ul class="form__field-list">
            <li class="form__field-item form__field-item--full">
              <label class="form__label" for="email">Email *</label>
              <input type="text" class="form__input form__input" id="email" data-bind="value: email" />
            </li>
            <li class="form__field-item form__field-item--full">
              <label class="form__label" for="message">Message *</label>
              <textarea class="form__input form__input--multiline" id="message" data-bind="value: message"></textarea>
            </li>
            <li class="form__field-item form__field-item--full">
              <label class="form__label--checkbox" for="isOptedIn">I would like occasional updates about Street Support in my inbox</label>
              <input type="checkbox" id="isOptedIn" data-bind="attr: { value: isOptedIn }, checked: isOptedIn" class="form__input--checkbox" />
            </li>
          </ul>
        </fieldset>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--brand-d form__submit" data-bind="click: submit"><span class="btn__text">Submit</span></button>
      </form>
      <!-- /ko -->

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
